  "title": "cad drafter cum bar bender schedule",
  "description": "<p></p><ul><li>Specialized as a technical professional responsible for creating construction drawing, structural details and precise reinforcing steel schedules (rebar) to ensure structural integrity and cost-efficient construction.</li><li>Create, update, and modify structural and architectural shop drawings using AutoCAD </li><li>Calculate total rebar weight and quantity from drawings for procurement and cost estimation.</li><li>Collaborate with project engineers, site managers, and sub-contractors to interpret structural designs and resolve site discrepancies.</li><li>Visit project sites to take measurements, verify and produce as-built drawings based on site adjustments.</li><li>Prepare shop drawings for submission to consultants and authorities, incorporating comments for final approval</li></ul><p></p>",
